graph TD
    A[Input Tensor x] -->|Weight w| Mult{Multiply}
    Mult -->|Bias b| Add{Add}
    Add --> Output[Prediction y]
    
    Output -.->|Loss Calculation| L[Loss Layer]
    L -.->|dLoss/db| Add
    L -.->|dLoss/dw| Mult
    
    style A fill:#f9f,stroke:#333
    style Output fill:#bbf,stroke:#333
    style L fill:#f66,stroke:#333,color:#fff
